KUZOZWELA  ephaketheni kubashayeli njengoba kwenyuka intengo ka-petrol okulindeleke ukuthi kuqale ngesonto elizayo futhi izobe yenyuke ngenani eliphezulu elingajwayelekile. UNgqongqoshe wezaMandla, uMnuz Jeff Radebe, uthe lokhu kwenyuka kwentengo ka-petrol kudalwa ukudonsa kanzima kwerandi uma liqhathaniswa ne-dollar. Ukhale nangentengo ka-oyela ongahluziwe athe umba eqolo emhlabeni wonke.  Ilitha lizobiza R14.72 isuka kuR14.23 nokuyinto ezobashaya kakhulu abashayeli. Kuthiwa le mbazo izoqala ngoLwesithathu. Udizili uzokwenyuka phakathi kuka- 58 kuya ku-59 ilitha. U-paraffin uzonyuka ngo-52c ilitha, i-gas inyuke ngo-70c ikhilo.